  <title>World Countries - Generalized</title>
  <abstract>World Countries Generalized represents generalized boundaries for the countries of the world.

World Countries Generalized provides generalized political boundaries for the world and includes most of the attribute fields found in the World Countries. The generalized political boundaries improve draw performance and effectiveness at a global or continental level.</abstract>
